summary: Mod adds a new playable race \"White Elf\"
descriptionHtml:
[center][IMG]http://i1080.photobucket.com/albums/j334/sphinxyro/white643164174.png[/IMG][/center]


[IMG]http://i1080.photobucket.com/albums/j334/sphinxyro/white1643174698.png[/IMG]
(sorry for my bad English)
White elves are small, slender, have a long golden hair perfectly
composing the golden eyes. With is height is ideal for assasin.
The Elves of this race receive bonuses for stealth, also have
an innate talent \"Shadow Cloak\" so they can become invisible.
Moreover, they are in the middle are resistant to disease and
poison the Silvan Elves cousins.

HP: 110
Stamina: 110
MP: 100
+ 2 racial abilities:
\"Shadow Cloak\" - Invisibility 120s/1day 
50% resistance to poison and 50% resistance to disease
+ five unique skin tone
+ 3 unique eye textures (female/male)

Bonus skills
===========
+10 one-handed
+10 sneak
+5 light armor
+5 alchemy
+5 enchanting
